reviewText: I'm so impressed with the Shadow Dancers dvds and this one is certainly no exception. With a push of a button, you have entertainment at its finest, combined in a quality box-set to take with you anywhere you go. Ideal for clubs, fetish parties, theme-nights, and more. Seriously, what guy would want to have sports on the screens when you can have these sexy shadow dancers to look at?
Been using Shadow Dancers visuals on our screens for years and they still get great feedback from men and women alike, so much better than having regular tv on.

This set is a must buy, we got it for our club in LA and we use it all year round, for the price we pay some crappy bands more on one night and get nothing back for it. This captivates our customers and that translates into more money over the bar. They light up a room and make for a good sensual but not innapropriate vibe. Never had a complaint, fellow Bar and Club owners, certain things only are must haves! This is a no brainer.
